**`*cn`* function should be used only in a case you are merging styles**:
className=’mr-4 pb-6’ ✅

className={cn(’mr-4 pb-6’)} ❌

**“Base” styles should be declared first, overriding - last:**

className={cn(’mr-4 pb-6’, props.className)} ✅

className={cn(props.className, ’mr-4 pb-6’ )} ❌

**Conditional classes should be declared this way:**

className={cn(’mr-4 pb-6’, {’border-5’: isBorderVisible})} ✅